Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.52,0:00:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.20,0:00:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.84,0:00:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是亚城木君短篇新作的NAME
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.52,0:00:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.22,0:00:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶~我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.57,0:00:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「REVERSI」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.93,0:00:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是关于什么的漫画呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.57,0:00:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是出现了黑恶魔和白恶魔就…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.40,0:00:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之很有趣 请先读一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但总不会比新妻老师的僵尸更有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.46,0:00:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好有趣！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个主人公的战斗场面画得好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.41,0:00:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和以往亚城木的作品不同的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次不再是邪道漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是以王道战斗漫画的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与此相对的 这次新妻君的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以僵尸为主人公并与人类战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以说是引入了邪道的王道战斗漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.92,0:00:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把邪道提升到王道的亚城木梦叶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:01:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在王道中引入邪道的新妻英二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.23,0:01:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说是新妻老师和亚城木老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互相带着对方的意识创作出来的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们之间相互产生了积极的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底谁会赢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是新妻君吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是输赢的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使两篇都可以刊登
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.32,0:01:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会在同一期上刊登吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果连续刊登的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.87,0:01:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.62,0:01:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短篇要准备三篇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.57,0:01:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还只有两篇而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.67,0:01:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我多拿些稿子来啊 快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！副编辑长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.04,0:01:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:13.17,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,480)\c&HFFFFFF&}周刊和月刊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「REVERSI」已经决定在4月17日发售的20期上刊登了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\an8}太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉我们提出这么强人所难的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为无论如何都想让佐佐木编辑长调走前能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 虽然突然让我看NAME的时候我有点吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是没理由不提交那么有趣的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是只有现在的亚城木梦叶才能画出来的王道战斗漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能让真城君接一下电话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真城
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在前一期上会刊登新妻君的短篇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样都会被比较一番的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为王道漫画来比较
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画风的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒目的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:03:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精彩场面的连页以及分格的张弛度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 看来你已经比我还清楚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油画出出色的原稿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新妻君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「ZOMBIE☆GUN」已经决定在19期刊登了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解！我终于迈出了走向世界的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后的一期上会刊登亚城木君的短篇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢~好想快点看到哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次亚城木君也挑战王道战斗漫画了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不辛辣了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是相当辛辣的王道战斗漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,nice亚城木梦叶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,nice辛辣的王道战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别太用功哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按现在的进度时间很充足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我明白 但我想画出比英二更好的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚豆发来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.59,0:04:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说已经确定担任女主角了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:05:00.43,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H3C3E3E&\3c&HEFF2EF&\frz-16\an8\move(852,340,850,265}新角色确定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:05:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经确定担任Young Kick「即兴12」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女主角经理人小眼的声优了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是人气相当高的足球漫画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们被打败了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被亚豆超过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要让她的第一个JACK作品女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自我们的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要让「REVERSI」动画化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给亚豆准备好女主角的位置！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz10.5\c&H7B7C78&\3c&HF5FBF7&\shad0\fs33\b0\pos(780,114)}Re：新角色确定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz10.5\c&H7B7C78&\3c&HF5FBF7&\shad0\fs33\b0\pos(710,276)}恭喜你！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz12\c&H7B7C78&\3c&HF5FBF7&\shad0\fs33\b0\pos(822,288)}又给了我很多干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz13.5\c&H7B7C78&\3c&HF5FBF7&\shad0\fs33\b0\pos(746,476)}我定会追赶上你来实现梦想！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚豆小姐将来要担当女主角的我们的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要让它成为声优亚豆美保的第一代表作！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是19期的样刊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「ZOMBIE☆GUN」上了封面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让短篇作品上封面 这还是头一遭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是新编辑长的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也说明对新妻君有十分大的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 特殊待遇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不甘心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只能超过他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超过连续20周保持第一完结「CROW」的新妻英二
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「ZOMBIE☆GUN」第1位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然已经有所预料 但是居然能拿这么多票
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新妻英二果然是牛人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是奔着世界第一去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:07:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是真的吗 雄二郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说叫我班长啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好好 班长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,692票
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说这是短篇的最高纪录
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英二果然不是盖的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然这样才是新妻英二啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我们的胜负还未见分晓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样 请你尽快画「ZOMBIE☆GUN」的连载NAME
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到开会之前 请尽全力画的尽可能出彩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.29,0:07:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 这么老实 你一点儿都不高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高兴并燃烧着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20号的本报
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「REVERSI」第1位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「PCP」第4
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第1位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说还刷新了短篇纪录
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是上周的「ZOMBIE☆GUN」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 是超过了「ZOMBIE☆GUN」的692票
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这周的「REVERSI」以694票刷新纪录
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇！给力！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给力啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才说我有自信嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乱说 你什么时候说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗 但我当时就觉得应该能行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要给香耶打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我给亚豆发短信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没想到一个礼拜就被刷新了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上头已经说用「ZOMBIE☆GUN」开始连载
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周就到NAME的截稿期限了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要因为这点小事就失去干劲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「REVERSI」也要进行连载吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…亚城木君还有「PCP」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:09:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要同时连载两部 从现状来看有困难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然要连载「ZOMBIE☆GUN」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也想让「REVERSI」连载吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经做好心理准备你们会这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会跟上面传达的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太感谢您了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连载用的第1话的NAME我们已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话请过目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有意思 比起短篇还要好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 比起「PCP」还能更上一个台阶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咋回事嘛 雄二郎… 不…班长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新妻他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输了两票 还说什么征服世界太可笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我还不能出连载NAME
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也太浪费了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班长 这是「REVERSI」的连载NAME
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 你放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新妻君和亚城木君每人两部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合计四部这种事明摆着不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 会连载「ZOMBIE☆GUN」和「REVERSI」中有趣的那部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会发生那种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑JACK的现状 肯定是优先新妻君的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优先自己负责的作家 这未免有点过分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.77,0:10:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底 亚城木君每周能画两部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁说不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哪来的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们是二人组
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们自己也说要画
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.76,0:10:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边两个 适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NAME无可挑剔很有意思 没有理由不让登吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们正在连载「PCP」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就让「PCP」完结
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能别说得这么轻巧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「PCP」可是打算出中学生编的人气漫画啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就同时连载两部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…的确有困难
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为连载「TRAP」的时候曾因过度疲劳住过院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让他们勉强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 瓶子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事想找您商量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于「REVERSI」的短篇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是以怎样的意向让他们刊登的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么处理「REVERSI」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓶子 这已经是你该决定的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 请容许我作为「周刊少年JACK」的编辑长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与「必胜JACK」编辑长商量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那之后就渺无音讯 是不是意味着无法上连载会议啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.48,0:11:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是服部先生打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「可不可以登在必胜JACK上」 我不太明白您的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「REVERSI」要在「必胜JACK」上连载吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:12:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 每月一回的话应该能和周刊的「PCP」两部同时连载主编是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「REVERSI」连载
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把「ZOMBIE☆GUN」的分镜提交到连载会议上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我已经完全明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我很狂傲的说了要创作出世界第一的漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的对手不是世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是亚城木老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「ZOMBIE☆GUN」的对手是「REVERSI」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 不是「PCP」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是「REVERSI」是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和登刊的杂志没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为明显是「REVERSI」更有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然打算竭尽全力让两部作品都在周刊上连载
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能在月刊「必胜JACK」上连载
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话真是松了口气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们来说这是最好的结果了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好的结果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我尽快介绍你们认识「REVERSI」的担当编辑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然在「必胜」上连载的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也必须要他们的人来做担当编辑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然知道你们同时连载两部作品会很吃紧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 也还请你们不要让「PCP」下滑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会比之前更加努力的去画「PCP」的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服部先生好像有点寂寞呐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 说实话我们也是想让服部来负责的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这么说的话 也只是我们的任性罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是没有办法的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能对作者和作品过分投入的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:14:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我真的很想做「REVERSI」的担当编辑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定能成为出色的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算在「周刊少年JACK」上也能成为顶梁柱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直伴随亚城木他们成长的我最清楚不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新妻君也说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起「PCP」明显是「REVERSI」更加有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 他们画出了这么让人期望的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但 说到底我们也只是个上班族
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能遵从上司的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了 这些我都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我还是想说我很想做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 真的很想做「REVERSI」的编辑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 本来的话 应该是我到你们那去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.37,0:14:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们特地跑过来真是对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还慌慌忙忙的整理了资料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中野现在是「必胜JACK」的副编辑长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:15:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让副编辑长来做我们的编辑 真是信心大增啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.74,0:15:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这边的阵容还比较薄弱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很期待「REVERSI」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才是 很高兴都够连载
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样以来就只有一部能开新连载啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣的只有新妻君的「ZOMBIE☆GUN」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就一部的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不这回的一部先放着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下次凑满三部再一起开怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「ZOMBIE☆GUN」应该尽早连载吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让「REVERSI」连载不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今 你还在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为担心亚城木君在周刊上同时连载两部会很吃紧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才放到「必胜」上的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让「PCP」在「必胜」上连载
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而「REVERSI」在JACK上连载
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 扭转已经决定的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 说不定有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:16:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两部新连载的话还说得过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 太形式主义了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在读者层广泛的「必胜」上内容有更大发挥空间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对「PCP」来说也是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「REVERSI」从票数来看可是比「ZOMBIE☆GUN」还要高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起「PCP」新妻君也更加在意「REVERSI」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能在「周刊少年JACK」上和「ZOMBIE☆GUN」一决高下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服部也是比起「PCP」更想担当「REVERSI」的编辑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服部他是这么说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.74,0:16:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不说我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是班长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是连载会议中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了 到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是现在我正和亚城木君在讨论啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让亚城木君也去连载会议？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 为什么连我们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去一趟比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就直问了  服部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对「REVERSI」在「必胜JACK」上连载有何看法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…能实现「REVERSI」连载我认为是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚城木君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万分的感谢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是问你们这些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是问「PCP」和「REVERSI」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想让哪部在「周刊少年JACK」上连载
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是把你们的真心话说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想在周刊上连载哪部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,R…「REVERSI」已经定下在「必胜」上连载…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就算问想在哪里连载
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服部 说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让「REVERSI」在「周刊少年JACK」上连载
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哲 连你都…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想在周刊上画「REVERSI」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将「PCP」放到「必胜JACK」连载
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「REVERSI」决定在「周刊少年JACK」上连载
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢…谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 都这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 比起这个 能听到服部先生的心声我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真城君 高木君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须将「REVERSI」变为「周刊少年JACK」的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这一定是能成为支柱的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:18:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我自说自话了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:19:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你做了一个很好的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「REVERSI」的潜力只有周刊才能发挥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「PCP」在自由度较高的我们这里发表才更有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班长们也说了同样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是雄二郎 他做班长的工作超过了我们的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道谢还太早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是「REVERSI」10周就完结了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两个可就都没立场了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让它成为顶尖的漫画的 绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 顶尖的会是「ZOMBIE☆GUN」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「ZOMBIE☆GUN」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「REVERSI」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真期待今后的「周刊少年JACK」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓶子 你变得很有JACK编辑长的样子了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「REVERSI」的连载转到「周刊少年JACK」上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:19:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 有干劲了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小河先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像说要完结一部现在连载的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.95,0:20:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以又可以来帮我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小河先生啊 他很可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 既然连载了2部 就得比之前更抓紧了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是再加一个人的话这个工作室是不是有点挤了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 移一移沙发的话应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我不想离开这个工作室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 所以我打算从爷爷那买下这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 那我也出一半的钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用啦 是叔叔的工作室嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想买下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最高 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在和那个女孩子交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,额 算是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然问这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 给你了 拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.57,0:21:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笔记本？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是信弘的日记
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.75,0:21:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒也称不上是日记 不过叙述了对某个女性的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我怎么能收这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的啦 没什么大不了的 你看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔和亚豆的妈妈中学也是同桌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H63736B&\an8\shad0\fs35\bord0\frz25\frx-2\move(612,188,524,65)\fad(500,0)}我想和春野美雪结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H63736B&\an8\shad0\bord0\fs35\frz25\fad(500,0)\move(682,336,594,213)}在那之前我会在笔记里记录下对她的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H63736B&\an8\shad0\bord0\frz25\fs35\frx-2\fad(500,0)\move(906,594,818,471)}然后 我认为变成老爷爷和老婆婆的时候\N如果还能一起笑着看这本\N笔记是最幸福的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:21:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来叔叔在想这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某种意义上来说这能妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 这不是妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔是认真在落实着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.48,0:22:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.79,0:22:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 收到了亚豆妈妈要和别人结婚的信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.26,0:22:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H63736B&\an8\shad0\bord0\frz17\fs30\fad(500,0)\pos(722,116)}今年生日当天也收到了春野的信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.26,0:22:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H63736B&\an8\shad0\bord0\frz17\fs30\fad(500,0)\pos(758,146)}她也想着我呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.26,0:22:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H63736B&\an5\shad0\frz17\fs40\fad(500,0)\pos(744,368)\3c&HE1EAE9&}一定要尽快成为一流的漫画家！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.26,0:22:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H63736B&\an8\shad0\bord0\frz17\fs30\fad(500,0)\pos(348,604)}计划都已经做好了\N只剩下决定求婚的话了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.26,0:22:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H63736B&\an8\shad0\bord0\frz17\fs30\fad(500,0)\pos(1072,518)}趁此给春野10封写好的信让她选择吧？…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.63,0:22:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是最后的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漫画家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔没能做成的事 想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.80,0:22:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来完成
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为JACK的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.03,0:24:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于要开始连载两部了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.80,0:24:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要把两部都画得很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.37,0:24:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是「REVERSI」可能坚持不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.05,0:24:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 延时和一鼓作气
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.43,0:24:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要选哪个梦想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
